  %article#diagnosis
    %h2 Diagnosis
    %a{:name => "diagnosis"}
    %p.p-slide
      The healthcare system in the U.S. needs improvement. While healthcare is complex and nuanced, other industrialized countries are performing much better than the U.S.. We spend $8,700 per capita
